 Understanding
 of the human mind

3
00:00:02,168 --> 00:00:04,402
 isn't complete unless it
 considers everything

4
00:00:04,403 --> 00:00:06,337
the brain is capable of.

5
00:00:06,338 --> 00:00:11,810
♪♪

6
