I'm a little anxious about
what's about to happen.

11
00:00:24,657 --> 00:00:28,093
This will probably be
a little bit uncomfortable.

12
00:00:28,094 --> 00:00:29,360
And my job?

13
00:00:29,361 --> 00:00:33,164
I'm the lab rat.

14
00:00:33,165 --> 00:00:34,732
 I'm about to head up
 the Amazon to drink

15
00:00:34,733 --> 00:00:36,868
 an ancient psychedelic drug.

16
00:00:36,869 --> 00:00:38,603
I would suggest that

17
00:00:38,604 --> 00:00:41,506
 you think about
 an emotional intention.

18
00:00:41,507 --> 00:00:42,307
To make it emotional

19
00:00:42,308 --> 00:00:44,209
is a lot more frightening
to me.

20
00:00:44,210 --> 00:00:45,443
♪♪

21
00:00:45,444 --> 00:00:48,480
 I started to see
 my body disappearing.

22
00:00:48,481 --> 00:00:50,248
♪♪

23
00:00:50,249 --> 00:00:52,884
 There was no going back.

24
00:00:52,885 --> 00:00:55,153
 You're forced to see
 the world differently,

25
00:00:55,154 --> 00:00:56,488
and by seeing the world
differently,

26
00:00:56,489 --> 00:00:59,390
 it makes you think
 differently.

27
00:00:59,391 --> 00:01:00,258
 What I wanna know is,

28
00:01:00,259 --> 00:01:01,893
if we put them
in front of a switch,

29
00:01:01,894 --> 00:01:03,862
 watching a train barrelling
 towards people,

30
00:01:03,863 --> 00:01:06,131
 would they actually
 pull it?

31
00:01:06,132 --> 00:01:09,234
I bet a lot of them
would freeze in that moment.

32
00:01:09,235 --> 00:01:11,569
♪♪

33
